## 2. User Stories
Format: "As a [persona], I want to [action], so that [benefit]"
- Group by epic
- Include acceptance criteria for each story
- Priority: Must/Should/Could/Won't (MoSCoW)

## 3. User Journey Maps
For each critical journey:
- Steps, touchpoints, emotions
